\v 15 K…ôn ek…ôk…ôike malkut p…®k roiu m…ôm…ô on…ôsotaluin…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n u nian oek…®m…®s r…ôk…®s.   
\p
\v 16 Nian emot…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô Iesu Kristo otuwa m…®n e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn, em…ôs…ôn…ôn namsu m…®n it…ôm suah kit t…ômol e r…ôhan …ôm n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn, m…ôto it…®m…ôhal em…ôhal…ôplan …ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…®t…®m…ôhal m…ôm…ô r…ôhan n…ôsan…ôn…ôn ne n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn in il…®s ag…®n.\x - \xo 1:16 \xt Mat 17:1-5 \x*  
\v 17-18 It…®mat min Iesu …ôp…ôh il…®s e n…®tot r…ôha Uhg…®n nian Uhg…®n Tata t…ômos-ip…ôn n…®siaii…ôn k…ôm in, k…ôn mol in n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn tasi…ô miet e n…®p…ôt…®n, k…ôn t…ôm…ôto n…ôwia Uhg…®n u N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn Asol t…ôm…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúInu n…ôt…®k it…ôm iakolkeike, n…®kik tagien p…®k ron.‚Äù It…®m…ôhal at…®p em…ôhal…ôto n…ôwian …ôh t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e nego e neai.\x - \xo 1:17-18 \xt Mat 17:5; Mak 9:7; Luk 9:35\x*   
\p
