\p
\v 4 It…ômat n…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô in otol nalp…®n…ôn …ôh m…ôto-inu n…ômot…ôplan nol…ôn r…ôhan aup…ôn. Nian nagelo m…®n k…ômotol t…ôfag…ô, Uhg…®n t…ôsask…ôl…®m …ôm…ôn r…ôhalat nalp…®n…ôn, m…ôto t…ôm…ôrakin-p…ôn ilat e n…®p…ôg asol teiuaiu ag…®n, ik…®n r…ôha net…ôm kot…ôrat, k…ôn t…ôm…ôlis ilat e sen, k…ôn kotat…®g e napin…ôp…ôn m…ôtoarus-pa in ot…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn o nalp…®n…ôn r…ôhalat.\x - \xo 2:4 \xt Jut 6 \x*  
\v 5 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôsask…ôl…®m-…ôm…ôn nalp…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ômim aup…ôn it…ôm k…ômoat…ôht n…ôwian e nian r…ôha Noah, m…ôto t…ômohamnu ilat e naru…ôh asol it…ôm t…ômaiu. M…ôto Noah t…ômat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha nol…ôn it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n, k…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômosmeg…ôh in, ne r…ôhan net…ômim sep…®n.\x - \xo 2:5 \xt Jen 6‚Äî8; 2 Pita 3:6 \x*  
\v 6 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômol nalp…®n…ôn o n…ôrat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Sotom ne Komora, k…ôn t…ômaan taon mil …ôh e n…®g…ôm, kioal n…ômtap lan. Inu tat…ôg…ôtun nat naka it…ôm otol k…ôm net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm koat…ôht n…ôwian.\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Jen 19:24; Jut 7 \x*  
