\v 8 K…ôn in t…ôm…ôtat…®g ilat min ilat, k…ôn nian rafin in t…ôm…ôplan nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhalat, k…ôn mat…ôto n…ôghat…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhalat, k…ôn nian rafin …ôm, n…®kin it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p …ôm, t…ômahm…ô p…®k o nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhalat.   
\p
\v 9 Nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Uhg…®n t…®tun nosmeg…ôh…ôn net…ômim it…ôm kotahat…ôt…ô lan, k…ôn t…®tun n…ômki-r…ôk…®s…ôn ilat e n…ôrat…ôn it…ôm kotat…®g lan. M…ôto net…ômim it…ôm k…ôsot…ôtuat…®p…ôn, Uhg…®n t…®tun nask…ôl…®m…ôn mol nalp…®n…ôn k…ôm ilat roiu muw…®n m…ôtoarus nian in ot…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn o nalp…®n…ôn r…ôha net…ômim.  
\v 10 Uhg…®n otol nalp…®n…ôn k…ôm net…ôm rat rafin, m…ôto in otol nalp…®n…ôn asol k…ôm net…ômim it…ôm koatol nat…®mnat r…ôha naul…®s…ôn it…ôm n…®p…ôt…®lat tolkeike m…ôm…ô okotol, k…ôn nat…®mnat u koatol ilat tamk…®m…®k, k…ôn net…ôm m…®n …ôh koatap…ôs n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn rafin.\x - \xo 2:10 \xt Jut 7-8,16 \x*  
\p Net…ôm m…®n …ôh kotausit m…ôsot…ôgin…ôn nat kit, k…ôn m…ôsot…ôgin…ôn n…ôn rat…ôn nat…®mnat e nego e neai it…ôm koat…ômeg…ôh u ilat il…®s p…®k.  
\v 11 Nat …ôpnap…®n nagelo m…®n, it…ôm ilat kot…ôsan…ôn k…ôn nahgilat tep…ôt tapr…ôk…®s-in net…ôm m…®n …ôh, m…ôto nagelo m…®n k…ôm…ôsot…ôhai…ôn nat…®mnat il…®s p…®k …ôh, m…ôsot…ôtu-p…ôn…ôn n…ôghat…ôn kit elat e n…®gan…ômt…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 2:11 \xt Jut 9 \x*  
\v 12 M…ôto net…ôm m…®n …ôh koat…ôn rat nat…®mnat it…ôm k…ôsot…®tun w…®r…ôn. Ilat kotahmen e nat iarup…®n m…®n, it…ôm r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…®k…ô, m…ôto koatol …ôm nat it…ôm n…®p…ôt…®lat tolkeike. Nat iarup…®n m…®n …ôh k…ômotaiir m…ôm…ô net…ômim okotarup…®n-in ilat motohamnu ilat. K…ôn Uhg…®n ot…ôr…ôk…®n m…®n net…ôm rat m…®n …ôh tahmen e nat iarup…®n m…®n …ôh.\x - \xo 2:12 \xt Jut 10 \x*  
\v 13 Uhg…®n ot…ôtou ilat e n…ôrat…ôn m…ôto-inu ilat k…ômotol n…ôrat…ôn k…ôm net…ômim.  
\p K…ôn i…ôg…ôtun eiueiu…ô m…®n …ôh, n…®kilat tagien m…ôm…ô okotagw…ôn ne mot…ôn…®m p…®k, s…ôn…ôm…ô lap…®n …ôm m…ôto e n…ôraui…ôg…ôn. Ilat kotahmen e nap…®n…ôn e n…®m…ôhan, o kotahmen e n…®m…ôg…ôm it…ôm tatol aul…®s it…ômat, moat…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôrg…® nim…ôfak. Kotuwa motagw…ôn it…ômat min ilat, m…ôto koateiu…ô-in it…ômat, moatol nol…ôn t…ôrat.  
\v 14 Nian rafin r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn tatuw…®n o nakl…ôh-in…ôn n…®p…®tan it…ôm r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…®m…ôt…®g …ôm, k…ôn nian rafin koatol t…ôfag…ô rat m…ôsotap…ôs…ôn. Koatiuw r…ôk…®s net…ômim it…ôm r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôtaliw…ôk-aliw…ôk, koatuw…®n e nol…ôn rat r…ôhalat. Ilat koat…ôg…ôtun at…®p ilat e nol…ôn r…ôha naum…®s…ôn. Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s nalp…®n…ôn r…ôhalat.  
\v 15 Ilat k…ômotap…ôs suat…®p it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p, k…ôn moteko mot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn suat…®p r…ôha Palam n…ôt…® Peor, it…ôm t…ômolkeike p…®k nos…ôn m…ôni e nol…ôn t…ôrat.\x - \xo 2:15 \xt Nam 22:7; Jut 11; Nol ∆èp…ôn 2:14 \x*  
\v 16 M…ôto togki kit t…ôm…ôhai o r…ôhan nol…ôn t…ôrat m…®n. Kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô togki t…ôs…ôghat…ôn, m…ôto Uhg…®n t…ômol m…ôm…ô togki tat…ôghat e n…®ki et…ômim m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-i…ôhau nol…ôn eko-eko r…ôha ien u.\x - \xo 2:16 \xt Nam 22:28-35 \x*   
\p
\v 17 I…ôg…ôtun eiueiu…ô m…®n …ôh kotahmen e n…ômt…® n…ôhau it…ôm t…ômam…®r, o kotahmen e n…®mal napu…ô it…ôm n…®m…ôtag asol t…ôm…ômki-r…ôk…®s, k…ôn nuhu…ôn t…®k…ô lan, m…ôto-inu n…ôg…ôtun…ôn r…ôhalat kot…ôrat. Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu kal…®n napin…ôp…ôn asol m…ôm…ô r…ôhalat.\x - \xo 2:17 \xt Jut 12-13 \x*  
\v 18 Ilat koat…ôghat ausit e n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm n…®p…ôt…®n t…®k…ô. Koat…ôghat e n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôha nol…ôn m…®n it…ôm n…®p…ôt…® net…ômim kotolkeike, k…ôn moatiuw-pa net…ômim kotuwa e n…ôrat…ôn it…ôm k…ômotiet wi …ôm lan.  
